#+title: Reliable Networks
* Network Architecture
Networks need to have 4 characteristics to meet user expectations:
- Fault Tolerance
- Scalability
- Quality of Service (QoS)
- Security

* Fault Toleranc
A network that is fault tolerant does not fall apart when one device fails.
